import React from 'react' import './Css/Contactus.css' import axios from 'axios'; const ContactForm = () => { const [formStatus, setFormStatus] = React.useState('Send') const onSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); setFormStatus('Submitting...'); const formData = new FormData(e.target); axios.post('/sav', formData) .then((response) => { if (response.status === 200) { setFormStatus('Submitted'); } else { setFormStatus('Error'); } }) .catch((error) => { console.error(error); setFormStatus('Error'); }); }; return (
